Packages
IVE_Editor Contains classes which makes the core of the editor.
IVE_Editor.Debug  
IVE_Editor.Design  
IVE_Editor.PlugIns Classes which enable mounting plug-ins (both components and moduls) into the editor and enables the comunication between them.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Components.Project Main classes for component project management.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Components.Project.Dialogs All dialog windows used by Project component.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Components.XMLLoader Main classes for XMLLoader component.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Components.XMLSaver Main classes for XMLSaver component.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL There is a main class of Modul of Objects and Locations (MOL) which handles its initialization and initialization of all of its parts.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.ClassManager Contains just one class which takes care about classes of ive objects.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.ExternEditors There are implemented all extern editors for object inspector.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.GUI All in this package has something in common with GUI of MOL.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.GUI.Collector This package makes and controles GUI of object collector and a repository which can be shown in it.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.GUI.GraphicInfo All graphic info classes cary information about appearance of some entity in view of the world (it is the black part of MOL's GUI where is shown the actually edited world as it will look in IVE).
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.GUI.GraphicManager There is an API for storing, creating and maintaining all graphic templates in current project.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.GUI.GraphicTemplates There is a GUI of graphic manager.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.GUI.Icons There are icons used by GUI of MOL.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.GUI.Inspector There is a GUI of object inspector and all necessary GUIs of objects properties which are the dynamic part of object inspector.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.GUI.ViewWorld This package with some huge classes contains the implementaion of view of the world.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.Inspector There is a model and controller of object inspector and implementation of the events which are sended in form of messages between parts of object inspector (these parts are parts of model-view-controller paradigm).
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.Kinds There are both model and view of kinds manager.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.Locations
In this package there is everything which concern the locations in editor.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.Log Classes for recording events into log and writing them into file.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.ObjectCollector There is a model of object collector which has stored all existing ive objects in the editor.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.Properties There are properties of ive objects.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MOL.Repository There is a model of repository of objects.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG MPG is main class for modul of processes and goals
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.EntGenius Specialized classes for EntGenius
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Gui Classes specialized for graphical user interface - Dialogs, Genies, Prosess, Tables, Links, SimmulationSettings, Utterances.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Gui.Dialogs Classes providing main part of the GUI for dialogs
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Gui.Genius Classes providing main part of the GUI for genies.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Gui.Icons Icons used by MPG.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Gui.Process Classes providing main part of the GUI for processes.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Gui.Tables Helper classses for easier work with the JTable SWING component.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Links Classes providing links.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.LocationGenius Specialized classes for LocationGenius.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Models Classes representing models of all tables for GUI.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Models.EntGenius Classes representing models of tables for EntGenines.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Models.LocationGenius Classes representing models of tables for LocationGenies.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Models.Process Classes representing models of tables for processes.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Process Huge group of classes for process managemet.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Repository Classes for repository management.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.SimulationSettings Classes for editing SimulationSettings element.
IVE_Editor.PlugIns.Moduls.MPG.Utterances Classes for utterances management.
